data.description: Fabulous opportunity for a family/friend compound or an investment opportunity to let you own for free. This 5.97 acre property offers a lovely 2 BR, 2 BA energy efficient home with open LIV-DIN-KIT with a gas range and SS refrigerator.  The covered front porch and back deck allow you to enjoy the peaceful property.  Extra storage in the attached workshop.  Guest cottage comes equipped as is so it is ready for your guests or AirBNB.  Recent property enhancements include a total of 8 full hook-up, RV sites.  One located behind the guest cottage and 7 mapped sites on the back of the property for RV's or Tiny Homes.  A 16x20 concrete patio near the back RV sites for gathering. The rear of the property has a gravel drive, additional septic, Bethel Ash water, and 400 amps of additional electric service.  The house, cottage, and 1 RV site are supported by their own 200 amps of power, septic, and water.  Plenty of room to add more sites or build a home. Great location!
